<div id="comments" class="comment-list hot show">
        <ul>
                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="1139162772">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-1139162772" class="vote-count">1</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-1139162772" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="1139162772">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/chuntiandejiuca/">东来</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
                    <span>2017-02-27</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">周汝昌，真才子，才情深深款款婉婉。这样执着于词本文韵来解诗词，其实吃力不讨好，解得不好，容易乏味，把诗味解没了，周汝昌解的好处在于他自己心性极浪漫自恋，解起来，虽按诗词的逻辑，但说到好处或开心处，不免发些高奇之论，有趣。看到后面发现夹带私货，扣一星。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="603712598">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-603712598" class="vote-count">2</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-603712598" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="603712598">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/64832870/">暖炉</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar50 rating" title="力荐"></span>
                    <span>2012-12-01</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">先生之诗心，用文白夹杂的话语道来，别有一番韵味，大概是最古典的讲法，以散文和诗来解诗。和旅居海外的叶嘉莹将西方现象学等融入诗词鉴赏的方式不同，周先生反感套入这些框架，失却其只可意会之妙也。数年语文古诗鉴赏课，实在抵不上一本书哎！</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="31021246">
